import { Col, Card } from 'react-bootstrap'


function MobileCard(props) {
    
    return (

        <>

            <Col lg={3}>
            <Card>
                <Card.Img style={{width: '80px'}} src={props.imageFileName} />
                <Card.Body>
                    <Card.Title>{props.name}</Card.Title>
                  
                        <Link to >
                            
                            </Link>
                    
                </Card.Body>
            </Card>
            </Col>
           
        </>

    )
}

export default MobileCard
